//TEXT
<jaT0001>October 17, 2046. It was exactly one year since that incident occurred. I had arrived too early, so I stood on the overlook gazing off into the distance.
<enT0001>October 17, 2046. It was exactly one year since that incident occurred. I had arrived too early, so I stood on the overlook gazing off into the distance.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>Today, memorial services were being held all across the country, but I came to participate in the military-sponsored ceremony being held here, at this airport.
<enT0002>Today, memorial services were being held all across the country, but I came to participate in the military-sponsored ceremony being held here, at this airport.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0003>"(We disobeyed orders in order to return, but now they're treating us like heroes... It was ridiculous.)"
<enT0003>"(We disobeyed orders in order to return, but now they're treating us like heroes... It was ridiculous.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0004>It seems there was a portion of the military who believed we should be strictly punished, but they were too afraid of public outcry to carry through.
<enT0004>It seems there was a portion of the military who believed we should be strictly punished, but they were too afraid of public outcry to carry through.

//TEXT
<jaT0005>Of course, it seems they were also afraid that certain facts they wanted to remain classified might be revealed if they held a court martial.
<enT0005>Of course, it seems they were also afraid that certain facts they wanted to remain classified might be revealed if they held a court martial.

//TEXT
<jaT0006>For example, I'm sure they wanted to hide the fact that the upper brass, who was "ruthless towards terrorists" according to the media, actually accepted their demands.
<enT0006>For example, I'm sure they wanted to hide the fact that the upper brass, who was "ruthless towards terrorists" according to the media, actually accepted their demands.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0007>"(Still... It's been a whole year since then...)"
<enT0007>"(Still... It's been a whole year since then...)"

//TEXT
<jaT0008>I looked up at the sky and let my emotions run. After we returned to Earth, every day passed by so fast it was hard to believe that a year had gone by.
<enT0008>I looked up at the sky and let my emotions run. After we returned to Earth, every day passed by so fast it was hard to believe that a year had gone by.

//TEXT
<jaT0009>We were hounded the press for a long time. Only recently was I able to live a normal life again...
<enT0009>We were hounded the press for a long time. Only recently was I able to live a normal life again...

//TEXT
<jaT0010>...Oh, I'm running out of time.
<enT0010>...Oh, I'm running out of time.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>I looked at my watch and realized it was almost time for me to meet up with her so I entered the airport and headed for our meeting spot.
<enT0011>I looked at my watch and realized it was almost time for me to meet up with her so I entered the airport and headed for our meeting spot.

//TEXT
<jaT0012>......
<enT0012>......

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0013>"Hey, Aki-chan."
<enT0013>"Hey, Aki-chan."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0014>"Sempai, you're late. You're far too late. You should never make a lady wait more than five minutes."
<enT0014>"Sempai, you're late. You're far too late. You should never make a lady wait more than five minutes."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0015>"I, I'm sorry. I arrived here early, but I lost track of time when I started thinking outside..."
<enT0015>"I, I'm sorry. I arrived here early, but I lost track of time when I started thinking outside..."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0016>"Hehe, of course I forgive you. You're rarely ever late for our meetings, Ryota-sempai."
<enT0016>"Hehe, of course I forgive you. You're rarely ever late for our meetings, Ryota-sempai."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0017>"Besides... It's been a whole year since then. I can understand wanting to feel sentimental about it..."
<enT0017>"Besides... It's been a whole year since then. I can understand wanting to feel sentimental about it..."

//TEXT
<jaT0018>Aki-chan's smile looked a little sad.
<enT0018>Aki-chan's smile looked a little sad.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0019>"Come on, don't look that that. A face like that doesn't suit you, Aki-chan."
<enT0019>"Come on, don't look that that. A face like that doesn't suit you, Aki-chan."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0020>"Ehe, you think so?"
<enT0020>"Ehe, you think so?"

//TEXT
<jaT0021>Aki-chan replied with a cheerful smile.
<enT0021>Aki-chan replied with a cheerful smile.

//TEXT
<jaT0022>Hmm, we've been dating each other for a year now, but she can finally smile honestly now. Her sarcasm is mostly gone and she rarely fights with Kazuhiko anymore either.
<enT0022>Hmm, we've been dating each other for a year now, but she can finally smile honestly now. Her sarcasm is mostly gone and she rarely fights with Kazuhiko anymore either.

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0023>"Anyways, Sempai, it's almost time for the ceremony. You'll be standing up addressing everyone, so you should get there early."
<enT0023>"Anyways, Sempai, it's almost time for the ceremony. You'll be standing up addressing everyone, so you should get there early."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0024>"Hah... I hate speeches."
<enT0024>"Hah... I hate speeches."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0025>"Hehehe, we can't help it. You're our leader after all."
<enT0025>"Hehehe, we can't help it. You're our leader after all."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0026>"Former. I'm not your leader anymore."
<enT0026>"Former. I'm not your leader anymore."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0027>"You're a man, so don't complain about every little detail. If you do, the women won't like you."
<enT0027>"You're a man, so don't complain about every little detail. If you do, the women won't like you."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0028>"...Eeh?!"
<enT0028>"...Eeh?!"

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0029>"Ehehe... Of course I'll still like you. After all, I just love, love, looove, you Ryota-sempai."
<enT0029>"Ehehe... Of course I'll still like you. After all, I just love, love, looove, you Ryota-sempai."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0030>"Aha, ahahahaha..."
<enT0030>"Aha, ahahahaha..."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0031>"Hehe, your face tells me you actually worried about it. Sempai, you worry too much."
<enT0031>"Hehe, your face tells me you actually worried about it. Sempai, you worry too much."

//TEXT
<jaT0032>Aki-chan grinned mischievously.
<enT0032>Aki-chan grinned mischievously.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0033>"B-but..."
<enT0033>"B-but..."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0034>"Well, let's drop this for now. Sempai, let's make our way to the reception hall. I'll come with you so you won't be as nervous."
<enT0034>"Well, let's drop this for now. Sempai, let's make our way to the reception hall. I'll come with you so you won't be as nervous."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0035>"Y-yea..."
<enT0035>"Y-yea..."

//TEXT
<jaT0036>I headed for the ceremony with Aki-chan pulling me along.
<enT0036>I headed for the ceremony with Aki-chan pulling me along.

//TEXT
<jaT0037>......
<enT0037>......

//TEXT
<jaT0038>...
<enT0038>...

//TEXT
<jaT0039>After the ceremony ended, I returned to my previous spot for a breath of air.
<enT0039>After the ceremony ended, I returned to my previous spot for a breath of air.

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0040>"Ryota-sempai, you're the type who can do it when they try. You looked kind of cool up there."
<enT0040>"Ryota-sempai, you're the type who can do it when they try. You looked kind of cool up there."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0041>"Ehen, was I amazing?"
<enT0041>"Ehen, was I amazing?"

//TEXT
<jaT0042>As I held my head up proud, I took a small envelope out of my uniform pocket.
<enT0042>As I held my head up proud, I took a small envelope out of my uniform pocket.

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0043>"What is that envelope?"
<enT0043>"What is that envelope?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0044>"I don't know. It arrived this morning and on the back there was a woman's handwriting. It read, 'Please open this after the ceremony is over.'"
<enT0044>"I don't know. It arrived this morning and on the back there was a woman's handwriting. It read, 'Please open this after the ceremony is over.'"

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0045>"...A woman? I won't forgive you if you're cheating on me."
<enT0045>"...A woman? I won't forgive you if you're cheating on me."

//TEXT
<jaT0046>Aki-chan glared at me with fearsome eyes.
<enT0046>Aki-chan glared at me with fearsome eyes.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0047>"Th-that's not it! I wouldn't do anything like that..."
<enT0047>"Th-that's not it! I wouldn't do anything like that..."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0048>"Hehe... I'm kidding. We've already been dating for a year... I'm well aware that you don't have the courage to do that, Sempai."
<enT0048>"Hehe... I'm kidding. We've already been dating for a year... I'm well aware that you don't have the courage to do that, Sempai."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0049>"Hahaha..."
<enT0049>"Hahaha..."

//TEXT
<jaT0050>I have mixed feelings about being considered a safe man... Hah...
<enT0050>I have mixed feelings about being considered a safe man... Hah...

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0051>"Hey isn't the view from here great?"
<enT0051>"Hey isn't the view from here great?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0052>"Yea... It is."
<enT0052>"Yea... It is."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0053>"Hey, Sempai? Can I look at the scenery for a while?"
<enT0053>"Hey, Sempai? Can I look at the scenery for a while?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0054>"Sure, I'll come with you."
<enT0054>"Sure, I'll come with you."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0055>"Yay! Thank you!"
<enT0055>"Yay! Thank you!"

//TEXT
<jaT0056>Aki-chan happily tugged on my hand as we walked.
<enT0056>Aki-chan happily tugged on my hand as we walked.

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0057>"......"
<enT0057>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0058>For a while, Aki-chan just silently stared off into the distance. She looked a little listless, but she also looked like she was truly enjoying it.
<enT0058>For a while, Aki-chan just silently stared off into the distance. She looked a little listless, but she also looked like she was truly enjoying it.

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0059>"......"
<enT0059>"......"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0060>"...Hey, Aki-chan?"
<enT0060>"...Hey, Aki-chan?"

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0061>"Yes? What is it?"
<enT0061>"Yes? What is it?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0062>"...What are you thinking about? Are you think about what happened one year ago?"
<enT0062>"...What are you thinking about? Are you think about what happened one year ago?"

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0063>"Wel... you're very close, but not quite."
<enT0063>"Wel... you're very close, but not quite."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0064>"I was actually thinking that this spot was where I first met your brother. I was remembering that a little bit."
<enT0064>"I was actually thinking that this spot was where I first met your brother. I was remembering that a little bit."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0065>"Ohh, I see..."
<enT0065>"Ohh, I see..."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0066>"......"
<enT0066>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0067>Even when I talked to her, Aki-chan continued to look off into the endless distance.
<enT0067>Even when I talked to her, Aki-chan continued to look off into the endless distance.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0068>"......"
<enT0068>"......"

//TEXT
<jaT0069>What should I do? She might say "I know" again, but I should...
<enT0069>What should I do? She might say "I know" again, but I should...

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0070>"...Hey, Aki-chan?"
<enT0070>"...Hey, Aki-chan?"

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0071>"Hehe... I know, Sempai. We have to live our lives for the sake of everyone else, right? I've heard you say that often enough over this past year. I can tell when you're leading into it now."
<enT0071>"Hehe... I know, Sempai. We have to live our lives for the sake of everyone else, right? I've heard you say that often enough over this past year. I can tell when you're leading into it now."

//TEXT
<jaT0072>Aki-chan smiled as she replied. She must have noticed my concern as I watched her.
<enT0072>Aki-chan smiled as she replied. She must have noticed my concern as I watched her.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0073>"Hahaha... I see. As long as you know then."
<enT0073>"Hahaha... I see. As long as you know then."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0074>"We should live our lives to the fullest and enjoy our bright, cheerful lives for everyone else."
<enT0074>"We should live our lives to the fullest and enjoy our bright, cheerful lives for everyone else."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0075>"Yes. That's right."
<enT0075>"Yes. That's right."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0076>"I'll do my best, so... please continue to stay by my side. I need you in my life, Sempai."
<enT0076>"I'll do my best, so... please continue to stay by my side. I need you in my life, Sempai."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0077>"Of course. I'll never let you go, Aki-chan."
<enT0077>"Of course. I'll never let you go, Aki-chan."

//TEXT 【Aki】
<jaT0078>"Thanks..."
<enT0078>"Thanks..."

//TEXT
<jaT0079>Aki-chan wore a happy, carefree smile.
<enT0079>Aki-chan wore a happy, carefree smile.

//TEXT
<jaT0080>That smile made me feel the happiness between us and I knew I wanted to keep protecting her.
<enT0080>That smile made me feel the happiness between us and I knew I wanted to keep protecting her.

//TEXT
<jaT0081>......
<enT0081>......

//TEXT
<jaT0082>...
<enT0082>...

